 returned to the battlefield.£6/8/2016: Abilities such as shroud and protection function only on the battlefield unless otherwise specified. A creature card with shroud may be targeted by Animate Dead, and Animate Dead will become attached to the creature that enters the battlefield.£6/8/2016: If the creature put onto the battlefield has protection from black—or if the creature can’t legally be enchanted by Animate Dead for another reason—Animate Dead won’t be able to attach to it. It will be put into the graveyard as a state-based action, causing its delayed triggered ability to trigger. When the trigger resolves, if the creature’s still on the battlefield, its controller will sacrifice it.£6/8/2016: Once the creature is returned to the battlefield, Animate Dead can’t be attached to anything other than it (unless Animate Dead somehow manages to put a different creature onto the battlefield). Attempting to move Animate Dead to another creature won’t work.','B',NULL,'0.9','1.51','2.2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B',NULL,NULL,'Animation des morts','Belebung der Toten','Animare i Morti',NULL,'Reviver Cadáver',NULL,'Animar a los muertos',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','Verzauberung','N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,'N/A','Wähle eine Kreaturenkarte in einem der Friedhöfe, wenn Du die Belebung der Toten sprichst. Wenn die Belebung der Toten ins Spiel kommt, bringe diese Kreatur unter Deiner Kontrolle ins Spiel, und die Belebung der Toten wird zu einer Kreaturenverzauberung,£die auf diese Kreatur zielt. Die verzauberte Kreatur erhält -1/-0. Wenn die Belebung der Toten das Spiel verlässt, begrabe die Kreatur.','N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,'N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('4102','Animate Wall','5E','Enchantment — Aura','R','{W}','1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Enchant Wall£Enchanted Wall can attack as though it didn''t have defender.','#_"When you have been bitten with fangs of granite, you start to long for th